WEBVTT

00:02.666 --> 00:03.374
Packing Up

00:04.650 --> 00:06.061
We're going camping!

00:07.157 --> 00:10.542
We pack our tent, sleeping bags, and cooking gear.

00:11.658 --> 00:13.953
"Don't forget the camera!" I say.

00:15.039 --> 00:17.955
We drive to the lake, and we set up camp.

00:18.964 --> 00:21.201
Click! I take a picture.

00:22.869 --> 00:23.851
Nighttime

00:24.913 --> 00:27.140
"Time to eat," says Dad.

00:28.222 --> 00:31.403
We build a fire to cook hamburgers and hotdogs.

00:32.447 --> 00:34.533
Click! I take a picture.

00:35.591 --> 00:37.953
"Time for bed," says Mom.

00:38.972 --> 00:41.083
We get into our sleeping bags.

00:42.126 --> 00:43.501
We look at the stars.

00:44.563 --> 00:46.509
Click! I take a picture.

00:48.148 --> 00:49.445
Bear and Fish

00:50.565 --> 00:53.355
In the morning, we see a bear by the lake.

00:54.495 --> 00:55.883
It is eating berries.

00:56.965 --> 00:58.901
Click! I take a picture.

00:59.930 --> 01:02.501
"Time for fishing," says Dad.

01:03.520 --> 01:06.987
Mom catches three fish, and Abby catches a turtle.

01:08.074 --> 01:10.219
Click! I take a picture.

01:11.799 --> 01:13.043
Time to Go Home

01:14.145 --> 01:17.767
Our camping trip is over, and it's time to go home.

01:18.795 --> 01:20.857
Click! I take a picture.

01:21.881 --> 01:25.727
The next day, Grandma wants to hear all about our trip.

01:26.741 --> 01:28.681
I can't remember everything . . .

01:29.638 --> 01:32.634
. . . so I show Grandma all my pictures!

